import React, {useState, useEffect} from 'react' import Footer from './Footer' import Header from './Header' import axios from 'axios' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { baseUrl } from './baseUrl' function Pastel() { useEffect(()=>{getLahangadata(); window.scrollTo(0,0)},[]) const navigate = useNavigate() const[ lahangaData, setLahangaData ] = useState([]) const getLahangadata=()=>{ axios.get(baseUrl+"product").then((res)=>setLahangaData(res.data.data.filter((i)=>i.category==="Kurtis"))) } return (
{lahangaData.map((i,n)=>
{navigate("/ProductView"); localStorage.setItem("productdata",JSON.stringify(i))}}>

)}
) } export default Pastel
